  "description": [
    "PAGE TEN Arizona Man Just Back From Russia Gives Vivid and FirstHand Story of Horror of Bolsheviki Rule In That Benighted Land PHOENIX Feb 14 We must make up our minds that we must whip bolshevism either in Russia or in the United States and God help us if we wait to whip it here Telling a gruesome story of what bolshevism has done in Russia and what it will do to every other coun try it touches that is the one con clusion of Captain Jay F Alkire of Phoenix head of the American Red Cross mission in south Russia one of two Americans in this country who have seen fully the reoent phases of bolshevism in interior Russia Cap tain Alkire arrived home this week after leaving Russia December 5 One other officer of the mission returned to this country with him Bolshevism means terror murder anarchy destruction for personal gain It means its power by mass terrorism That is the way Captain Alkire summed up bolshevism giving a first hand account a tale of horror almost unbelievable of the working of that mighty disease which withers all it touches And if that disease is not crushed in"
  ],
